  "bodyHtml": "<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">Have you ever wanted to see the costs associated with each order you sell on Back Market? We’re making it easier for you to do this!</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">Now you can see the cost breakdown of each order.</span></span></span></span></span></span><br><br><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">To see the cost breakdown, go to “Orders” &gt; “More details” &gt; “Cost breakdown”.</span></span></span></span></span></span><br><br><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">You’ll see all costs here, from the sale price to refund amount and more — all in one place.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<span style=\"font-size: 10pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">Note that for technical reasons, some costs won&#39;t be available in the cost breakdown section including sales fee refunds, BackShip fee cost corrections, Customer Care by Back Market fee cost corrections, and more. We’re doing our best to include these costs in the future.</span></span></span></span></span></span><br> \n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"auto\" allowfullscreen=\"\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/M7XAoU128gw?si=y7grlWC7_FyTG9Ny\" title=\"YouTube video player\" width=\"560\"></iframe></div>\n\n\n\n<div id=\"\" style=\"left: 72.9167px;top: 258.711px;\"> </div>"
